institutions around the world,

00:00:46.660 --> 00:00:49.750
from the University of
Ghana, Hong Kong University,

00:00:49.750 --> 00:00:53.750
King's College London and Yale
University to pick just one each

00:00:53.750 --> 00:00:58.110
