talk about music.

00:02:09.760 --> 00:02:13.950
His next book continues to work
he began in playing with science,

00:02:13.950 --> 00:02:17.780
Music Is Discourse Semiotic
Adventures And Romantic Music.

00:02:17.780 --> 00:02:21.500
It shows Dr. Agawu's unique
approach to dealing with questions

00:02:21.500 --> 00:02:24.500
of musical meaning
in romantic music.

00:02:24.500 --> 00:02:26.730
Prof. Agawu's latest
book from which the topic

00:02:26.730 --> 00:02:31.700 position:56%
of this evenings lecture is drawn
