00:58:37.140 --> 00:58:39.300
If the shapes of African rhythm

00:58:39.300 --> 00:58:42.880
that we've been exploring
today are anything to go by,

00:58:42.880 --> 00:58:47.100
complete with their
silence, or short down beats,

00:58:47.100 --> 00:58:51.520
their symmetry disrupting kinks,
their nonalignment between grouping

00:58:51.520 --> 00:58:57.090
and meter and so on, then Hancock's
appropriation imposes as I said,

00:58:57.090 --> 00:59:02.330
